{"title":"遐想","authors":["晓凡"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":4,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"遐想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓凡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银须，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹤发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双大手腰间插；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅挺立地图前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一尊铁塔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅望三峡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，黄河浪涛在喧哗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涛声在笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涛声在夸："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸咱送去好钢材，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铸就了万古不移拦洪坝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞩目高原上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心随情飞到拉萨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身农奴收青稞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗颗汗珠落地下；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边地呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望机械化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！祖国大地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少高山要削平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少煤层等待风镐去开挖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少江河静候铁桥跨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少个新兴的地区呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要我们这代人往那地图上画！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地图前遐想无边涯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心头升起万丈霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光照普天下；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顿足转身回工段，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车刀下飞迸出灿烂金花！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}